data.text: @AjeerahFareha Tu lah ada baca dengan adik izzat sebab kau balik kejap kan weekend tu. InsyaAllah tak ada apa
@atirararararara Bukan dgn cu. dgn adik izzat. Haha tp so far asymptomatic. Aku risau kat Anggun je ni 😕
@AjeerahFareha Thank youuu ❤️ korang okay ke? Close contact juga kan?

Much better than first day. Able to get up and walk a bit more sebab sakit badan dah kurang. Semuanya bertambah baik kecuali sakit tekak. So far so good! Dah tu je kbye

xoxo,💋

Still fever at 38.2° in the morning. Lepas makan ubat rest jap lepas tu dah start peluh mandi and feeling good again. Nasi lemak sebungkus lauk ayam goreng + sambal sotong (thanks to my husband and MIL) 😘

Fever reduce (36.8°) in the evening dah kerjanya tidur jeeee 🤪

DAY-2
Bangun pagi tekak makin perit so get my husband to prepare lemon drink but still the same satu hari struggle menelan. Walaupun sakit tekak makan macam biasa (dah tu je mampu dibuat 😆)
PCR result up malam semalam. CT value agak rendah. Walaubagaimanapun, kuey teow sup semangkuk tetap licinnnnnnnn https://t.co/6DsGWjbMqu
